    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A cone of biting cold air deals significant cold damage to everyone in it.</em></p><p>A blast of cold air erupts from your hands. Each creature in a 60-foot cone must make a CON save. A creature takes 8d8 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>A creature killed by this spell becomes a frozen statue until it thaws.</p><p><em><strong>At Higher Rings.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th ring or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot beyond 5th ring.</p>",
